description:
Here's how to make a simple but tasty Adobo dish, Kale Adobo with Jackfruit. This dish is part 2 of the Adobo Series. 

Ingredients list:
3 tbsp refined coconut oil (12 tbsp melted)
4 cloves of garlic, crushed and minced
1 bunch curly kale, stems removed
1 can jackfruit in syrup
1 tbsp. jackfruit syrup
3 tbsp. soy sauce

Part 1 :https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yGwkaZrk_Kk

For more info and tips, visit http://astigvegan.com

Kain na, let's eat!
